ROCK SOLID INDUSTRIES.  ROCK SOLID STRONG

RSI Flat Rack

  • Black epoxy powder-coated T6 aluminium
  • Approximate Installed Weight of RSI Flat Rack  20kg
  • T Slot Extrusions
  • Universally Compatible with M8 Bolt accessories.

 

Amarok

Dimensions: 1300mm  x 1260mm x 90 mm

Ranger / Hilux / D-Max / Bt-50

Dimensions: 1300mm  x 1156mm x 90 mm

USA Trucks

Dimensions: 1500mm  x 1356mm x 90 mm

 

Click here to view the entire range of RSI SmartCap Evo Canopies available!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!

 

Please note: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order.
